{{- $mod        := "Ctrl+Shift"     -}}
{{- $mod_shift  := "Ctrl+Shift+Alt" -}}
{{- $mod_opt    := "Alt"            -}}
{{- $mod_ctrl   := "Ctrl+Alt"       -}}
{{- $mod_resize := "Ctrl+Shift"     -}}
{{- if eq .chezmoi.os "darwin" -}}
{{-   $mod         = "Cmd"       -}}
{{-   $mod_shift   = "Cmd+Shift"  -}}
{{-   $mod_opt     = "Cmd+Opt"    -}}
{{-   $mod_ctrl    = "Cmd+Ctrl"   -}}
{{-   $mod_resize  = "Cmd+Ctrl"   -}}
{{- end }}
# WezTerm shortcuts ({{ .chezmoi.os }})

Press `q` to close this window.

## Panes
| Action                | Shortcut |
| --------------------- | -------- |
| Split horizontal      | `{{ $mod }}+D` |
| Split vertical        | `{{ $mod_shift }}+D` |
| Close pane            | `{{ $mod }}+W` |
| Zoom pane             | `{{ $mod_shift }}+Z` |
| Navigate (←↑↓→)       | `{{ $mod_opt }}+Arrow` |
| Resize (±5 cells)     | `{{ $mod_resize }}+Arrow` |

## Tabs
| Action                | Shortcut |
| --------------------- | -------- |
| New tab               | `{{ $mod }}+T` |
| Jump to tab N         | `{{ $mod }}+1` .. `{{ $mod }}+9` |
{{- if eq .chezmoi.os "darwin" }}
| Next tab              | `{{ $mod_shift }}+]` |
| Prev tab              | `{{ $mod_shift }}+[` |
{{- else }}
| Next tab              | `Ctrl+Tab`  ·  `Ctrl+PageDown` |
| Prev tab              | `Ctrl+Shift+Tab`  ·  `Ctrl+PageUp` |
{{- end }}
| Rename tab            | `{{ $mod_shift }}+R` |

## Font size
| Action                | Shortcut |
| --------------------- | -------- |
| Increase              | `{{ $mod }}+=` |
| Decrease              | `{{ $mod }}+-` |
| Reset                 | `{{ $mod }}+0` |

## Search & selection
| Action                | Shortcut |
| --------------------- | -------- |
| Search scrollback     | `{{ $mod }}+F` |
| Next match            | `{{ $mod }}+G`  (in search) |
| Prev match            | `{{ $mod_shift }}+G`  (in search) |
| Quick select          | `{{ $mod_shift }}+Space` |

## Window & system
| Action                | Shortcut |
| --------------------- | -------- |
| Toggle fullscreen     | `{{ $mod_ctrl }}+F` |
| Reload config         | `{{ $mod_ctrl }}+R`  (or just save the file) |
| Open this config      | `{{ $mod }}+,` |
| Show this help        | `{{ $mod_shift }}+H` |

## Shell input
| Action                | Shortcut |
| --------------------- | -------- |
| Delete previous word  | `Ctrl+Backspace`  (sent as Ctrl+W to readline) |
